snippet: Rory McIlroy, 22, won the Honda Classic and became the youngest golfer to claim the No. 1 ranking since Tiger Woods in 1997.
abstract: Rory McIlroy wins the Honda Classic golf tournament; becomes the youngest golfer to claim the No. 1 ranking since Tiger Woods in 1997.
lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy, 22, won the Honda Classic and became the youngest golfer to claim the No. 1 ranking since Tiger Woods in 1997.

headline.seo: Rory McIlroy Beats Tiger Woods at Honda Classic
headline.main: McIlroy Holds Off Woods and Shows Who’s No. 1
